SenStore::Int64Array

Overview

struct Int64Array

Multi-dimensional array data. Note that the vector data must be reshaped to get the multi-dimensional array. In Python, use: a = numpy.array(myStruct.data); a = a.reshape(myStruct.shape);

Data Member Index

shape
Array dimensions (shape).
data
Array data, stored as a vector.

Data Members

DimensionList shape;

Array dimensions (shape).

Int64List data;

Array data, stored as a vector.
